---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Études Environnementales & Publications"
permalink: /etudes/
description: "Expertise technique sur les conventions BRS, Minamata, CCNUCC et SAICM en République du Congo."
keywords: "études environnementales Congo, conventions BRS, mercure Congo, climat Congo, expertise écologique"
hero:
  title: "Nos Travaux d'Études"
  subtitle: "À ce jour l'AED, a contribué à la mise en œuvre au Congo des publications et recherches sur les conventions environnementales."
---

<section class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-banner-content">
            <h1>{{ hero.title }}</h1>
            <p><span class="highlight">{{ hero.subtitle }}</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% include "partners-banner.html" %}

<div class="main-content section-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="convention-filters">
            <button class="conv-btn active" data-conv="brs">BRS</button>
            <button class="conv-btn" data-conv="minamata">Minamata</button>
            <button class="conv-btn" data-conv="ccnucc">CCNUCC</button>
            <button class="conv-btn" data-conv="saicm">SAICM</button>
            <button class="conv-btn" data-conv="cirgl">CIRGL</button>
        </div>

        {% set conventions = ["brs", "minamata", "ccnucc", "saicm", "cirgl"] %}
        
        {% for conv in conventions %}
        <div id="conv-{{ conv }}" class="convention-section {% if loop.first %}active{% else %}hidden{% endif %}">
            <div class="content-header">
                <img src="/images/{{ conv | upper }}.jpg" alt="{{ conv | upper }}" class="conv-header-img" onerror="this.src='/images/logo.jpg'">
                <div>
                    <h2>Convention {{ conv | upper }}</h2>
                    <p>
                        {% if conv == "brs" %}Bâle, Rotterdam et Stockholm : gestion des déchets dangereux et des polluants organiques persistants.
                        {% elif conv == "minamata" %}Convention de Minamata sur le mercure : protéger la santé humaine et l'environnement des émissions de mercure.
                        {% elif conv == "ccnucc" %}Changements Climatiques : atténuation et adaptation face au réchauffement climatique.
                        {% elif conv == "saicm" %}Approche Stratégique de la Gestion Internationale des Produits Chimiques.
                        {% elif conv == "cirgl" %}Conférence Internationale sur la Région des Grands Lacs : gestion durable des ressources naturelles.
                        {% endif %}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="studies-list">
                {% set conv_studies = collections.studies | filterByConvention(conv) %}
                {% for study in conv_studies %}
                <article class="study-card">
                    <div class="study-header">
                        <div style="flex:1;">
                            <h3>{{ study.data.title }} {% if study.data.pdf %}<span class="pdf-indicator">📄 PDF</span>{% endif %}</h3>
                            <div class="study-meta">
                                <span>📅 {{ study.data.year }}</span>
                                <span>✍️ {{ study.data.authors }}</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="badge badge-{{ study.data.status }}">
                            {% if study.data.status == "published" %}Publié
                            {% elif study.data.status == "progress" %}En cours
                            {% else %}{{ study.data.status }}{% endif %}
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="study-body">
                        <p>{{ study.data.desc }}</p>
                        {% if study.data.pdf %}
                        <div class="actions">
                            <a href="{{ study.data.pdf }}" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">📥 Télécharger PDF</a>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </article>
                {% else %}
                <div class="empty-state">
                    <p>Aucune étude disponible pour cette convention.</p>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>

{% set scripts %}
<script src="/js/studies.js"></script>
{% endset %}
